==English==
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# A type of [[island]] consisting of a ribbon [[reef]] that nearly or entirely surrounds a [[lagoon]] and supports, in most cases, one to many [[islet]]s on the reef platform.  Atolls have a unique geology, so all islands with a reef and a lagoon are not atolls.
  
